NOTICE — Third-party dependencies and inspirations

This software depends on, but does not vendor or modify, the following projects:

- Raven (https://github.com/The-Commit-Company/Raven) — AGPL-3.0
  raven_ai_agent requires Raven to be installed on the same Frappe site.
  No Raven source code is included or modified in this repository.

This software draws design inspiration (patterns and concepts only, no code)
from the following permissively-licensed projects:

- KorucuTech/kai (https://github.com/KorucuTech/kai) — MIT
  Persona-triad design pattern (role, goal, backstory).
- sanjay-kumar001/ai_chatbot (https://github.com/sanjay-kumar001/ai_chatbot) — MIT
  Token cost tracking concept.
- OpenTelemetry trace data model (https://opentelemetry.io/docs/specs/otel/trace/api/) — Apache-2.0
  Audit log shape (trace_id, span_id, attributes, status).

Optional runtime integrations (deployed alongside but not vendored):

- frappe/mcp (https://github.com/frappe/mcp) — MIT
- rakeshgangwar/erpnext-mcp-server (https://github.com/rakeshgangwar/erpnext-mcp-server) — MIT
